<emphasis box="[430,606,582,606]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="372">macrophthalma</emphasis>
Stingelin&quot;. We believe that he mis-spelled this Stingelin's taxon; correct name is &quot; 
<taxonomicName box="[256,418,619,643]" class="Branchiopoda" family="Moinidae" genus="Moina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diplostraca" pageId="6" pageNumber="372" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="macrophtalma">
